'''古田山国家级自然保护区'''位于中国[[浙江省|浙江省]][[开化县|开化县]]，属于[[白际山脉|白际山脉]]的一部分，与[[江西省|江西省]][[婺源县|婺源县]]、[[德兴市|德兴市]]毗邻，总面积8,107公顷。主峰青尖海拔1,258米，为典型的[[江南古陆|江南古陆]]强烈上升的[[山地|山地]]地貌，属中亚热带湿润季风区<ref name=biods2015083>{{cite journal|last1=Hu|first1=Xiaoli|last2=Chang-Yang|first2=Chia-Hao|last3=Mi|first3=Xiangcheng|last4=Du|first4=Yanjun|last5=Chang|first5=Zhaoyang|title=Influence of climate, phylogeny, and functional traits on flowering phenology in a subtropical evergreen broad-leaved forest, East China|journal=Biodiversity Science|date=2015|volume=23|issue=5|pages=601–609|doi=10.17520/biods.2015083}}</ref>。主要保护对象是[[白颈长尾雉|白颈长尾雉]]和[[黑麂|黑麂]], 以及典型的[[亚热带常绿阔叶林|亚热带常绿阔叶林]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Peng |first1=Ren |last2=Jianping |first2=Yu |last3=Xiaonan |first3=Chen |last4=Xiaoli |first4=Shen |last5=Xiao |first5=Song |last6=Tiantian |first6=Zhang |last7=Yongquan |first7=Yu |last8=Ping |first8=Ding |title=Seasonal variation in the distribution of Elliot’s pheasant (Syrmaticus ellioti) in Gutianshan National Nature Reserve |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2019-01-20 |volume=27 |issue=1 |pages=13 |doi=10.17520/biods.2018193}}</ref>。

古田山年平均温度15.3℃，[[无霜期|无霜期]]约250天。年平均降水量1,963.7毫米，每年3–6月为第一雨季, 7–8月为伏旱期, 8月底到9月为第二雨季, 10月到翌年2月为干季<ref name=biods2015083 />。

[[土壤|土壤]]类型有[[红壤|红壤]]、[[红黄壤|红黄壤]]、[[黄红壤|黄红壤]]及[[高山草甸土|高山草甸土]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Zhang |first1=Tiantian |last2=Wang |first2=Xuan |last3=Ren |first3=Haibao |last4=Yu |first4=Jianping |last5=Jin |first5=Yi |last6=Qian |first6=Haiyuan |last7=Song |first7=Xiaoyou |last8=Ma |first8=Keping |last9=Yu |first9=Mingjian |title=A comparative study on the community characteristics of secondary and old-growth evergreen broad-leaved forests in Gutianshan, Zhejiang Province |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2019-10-20 |volume=27 |issue=10 |pages=1069 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019059}}</ref>。

